title: 19 Corporate Logo Tattoos That Make Us Go 'Why?'
text:
19 Corporate Logo Tattoos That Make Us Go 'Why?' Tweet Posted: Sat, 2/25/2017 - 9:37pm by Daniel Dominguez 
Bad corporate tattoos are definitely out there , but what I want to know is why anyone would get some corporation’s logo tattooed on them in the first place? Is mediocre coffee so important to you that you need a permanent reminder of the coffee shop you frequent? Is your memory just that bad that you might forget? I can’t understand why people would pay an artist to put a corporate logos on them. So here’s a bunch for you to judge. Maybe you can explain it to me? 1. Oct 30, 2014 at 11:22am PDT 2. May 17, 2014 at 8:49am PDT 3. Apr 9, 2016 at 8:13pm PDT 4. Jan 28, 2015 at 9:21pm PST 5. Jun 13, 2015 at 3:04pm PDT 6. Aug 25, 2016 at 2:54pm PDT 7. Feb 16, 2013 at 3:52pm PST 8. Jul 28, 2016 at 3:11pm PDT 15. Feb 19, 2017 at 11:47am PST 16. Aug 3, 2016 at 11:38am PDT 17. Feb 13, 2017 at 12:52pm PST 18. Dec 1, 2016 at 9:22pm PST 19. Jan 14, 2017 at 2:21am PST 
Why would anyone do this? If you have an explanation please let us know on Twitter @Smosh !
